# Transmission API

## Group Transmission
Endpoints for managing the Transmission container.

### Transmission Status [/transmission/]
#### Get Status [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
                "status": "running"
            }

### Start Transmission [/transmission/start]
#### Start Container [POST]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
                "message": "Transmission container started"
            }

### Stop Transmission [/transmission/stop]
#### Stop Container [POST]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
                "message": "Transmission container stopped"
            }
